OL,3,GHighlands & Eilean Siar
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FA largely cloudy start, but
OL,6,Fbright over the west coast and
OL,7,FHebrides. Brightening up through the
OL,8,Fday with sunny intervals developing
OL,9,Ffor all. Warm, locally very warm in
OL,10,Fthe west.
OL,11,
OL,12,CTonight:FA dry, warm and mostly sunny
OL,13,Fevening. Remaining dry with clear
OL,14,Fspells overnight but becoming chilly
OL,15,Fin the east with some patchy mist and
OL,16,Ffog.
OL,17,
OL,18,CMonday:FAny early mist in the east
OL,19,Fwill quickly clear then a dry day with
OL,20,Fplenty of warm sunshine. Becoming very
OL,21,Fwarm again in the west.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
