OL,3,GHighlands & Eilean Siar
OL,4,
OL,5,COutlook for Tuesday to Thursday:FA dry
OL,6,Ffew days with good spells of sunshine.
OL,7,FVery warm in the west with the best of
OL,8,Fthe sunshine, cloudier and cooler at
OL,9,Ftimes in the east.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
